      "de": "Schichtplan",
      "en": "Shift Plan"
    },
    "desc": {
      "de": "Flexibler Schichtkalender: 21-Tage-Modell, benutzerdefinierte Muster, Urlaubsverwaltung, Countdown, Wochenübersicht",
      "en": "Flexible shift calendar: 21-day model, custom patterns, vacation management, countdown, weekly overview"
